}}Ninety Six is the 187th largest city in the state of South Carolina, placing it in the middle of the state's city population rankings.{{failed verification|date=June 2025|See 2nd GA review for details}} As recorded in the 2020 census, Ninety Six had 2,076 residents, the highest count in town's history.{{failed verification|date=June 2025|See 2nd GA review for details}} Between 2010 and 2020, the town gained only 78 residents.{{failed verification|date=June 2025|See 2nd GA review for details}} In 2020, there were 706 households, and 520 families residing in the town.<ref name=":10" />{{failed verification|date=June 2025|See 2nd GA review for details}}

